features: 【Compact and Portable】The car tissues cylinder is suitable for most car cup holders and door storage compartments. The dimensions of the car tissue box are 2.6x7.2 inches, and the tissue size is 6.5x7.2 inches, providing convenience for daily commuting without taking up too much space.

【User-Friendly Design】The car tissue features a top cover that can be closed to keep the tissues waterproof and dustproof when not in use. It also has an internal barrier that allows for easy extraction of tissues. After using up the tissues, you can open the lid to replace them with new ones, which is both environmentally friendly and practical.

【Premium Materials】The tissues are made from 100% natural virgin pulp, ensuring that they are soft and durable with 3-ply thickness. They are perfect for wiping dust and cleaning food residue inside the car, making them suitable for both household and in-car use.

【Environmental Consciousness】We promote an eco-friendly concept and have designed the tissue holder with a natural and rustic style. The inspiration and concept of the design come from trees, soil, water and air. The car round tissue box looks like a decorative item, serving as a constant reminder to cherish nature and protect the environment.

【Versatile Use】Our car tissue holder is not only suitable for car cup holders but also for cafes, offices, living rooms, bathrooms, and more. By simply placing it, you can make the overall space look tidier and more organized.(If you have any questions after receiving the product, please feel free to contact us via email.)

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient and lightweight!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Carsonworks Cupholder Tissue and I must say, it has exceeded my expectations in every way. One of the standout features is its perfect fit for the side mesh pocket of my backpack. This clever design makes it incredibly convenient to access tissues whenever I need them without rummaging through my bag. Also its compact size and lightweight construction ensure that it doesn't add any bulk to my backpack. This is a game-changer, especially during long hikes or when I'm on the move. I can confidently say that the Carsonworks Cupholder Tissue is a must-have accessory for anyone who loves outdoor activities.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Very poor quality
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these because they're described as refillable and thought they'd be perfect in the doors of the car. Unfortunately they arrived crushed. This was not due to handling but because they're not made from sturdy cardboard tubing but instead from flimsy card stock. And though designed for refill and reuse they are simply too flimsy to survive long enough for refilling. I'm going to back engineer using the sturdy plastic caps with trimmed to size mailing tubes. I'll decorate the outside with decorative paper or acrylic paints so I'll still get some practical use from them...
